# Telegram Mini App Rules

## Authentication Source

Telegram Mini App SDK

## Requirements

- Validate initData
- Validate Telegram signature
- Auto create user
- Auto update profile data

## Store

- telegram_id
- username
- first_name
- last_name
- photo_url

## Never use

- Email Login
- Password Login
- Google Login

## Communication Rules

### Primary Contact Method

Telegram Bot Messaging

### Identity

- Never require Telegram username
- Use Telegram ID as the unique identifier
- Username optional
- Phone optional
- Telegram ID required

### Flow

Buyer
→ Contact Seller
→ Bot forwards message
→ Seller replies
→ Bot forwards reply to buyer

### Privacy & Routing

- Do not expose seller Telegram ID publicly
- All communication must go through the bot

Always trust Telegram identity as the primary user identity.
